      <p><a href="ch70s10.html#MonstersO-R80">Phase spiders</a> are aggressive predators that can move quickly from the Ethereal Plane to attack opponents on the Material Plane.<a href="img/MonstersO-R.Phase_Spider.jpg" target="_blank"><span class="inlinemediaobject"><img src="thumb/MonstersO-R.Phase_Spider.jpg" align="right"/></span></a></p>
      <p>A typical <a href="ch70s10.html#MonstersO-R80">phase spider's</a> body is 8 feet long. It weighs about 700 pounds.</p>
      <p><a href="ch70s10.html#MonstersO-R80">Phase spiders</a> cannot speak.</p>
      <div class="sect4" lang="en">
        <div class="titlepage">
          <div>
            <div>
              <h5 class="title"><a name="id2130973"/>Combat</h5>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="keywordset" style="display:none">
          <div class="keyword">monsterinfo</div>
        </div>
        <a class="indexterm" name="MonstersO-R81"/>
        <p><a href="ch70s10.html#MonstersO-R80">Phase spiders</a> dwell and hunt on the Material Plane. Once a spider locates prey, however, it shifts to the Ethereal Plane to attack, attempting to catch its victim flat-footed. The spider shifts in, bites its victim, and retreats quickly back to the Ethereal Plane.</p>
        <div class="simplesect" lang="en">
          <div class="titlepage"/>
          <a name="id2131006"/>
          <div class="keywordset" style="display:none">
            <div class="keyword">other</div>
          </div>
          <a class="indexterm" name="MonstersO-R82"/>
          <p><span class="strong"><strong>Ethereal Jaunt (Su):</strong></span> A <a href="ch70s10.html#MonstersO-R80">phase spider</a> can shift from the Ethereal Plane to the Material Plane as a free action, and shift back again as a move action (or during a move action). The ability is otherwise identical with <span class="emphasis"><em><a href="ch45.html#SpellsD-E70">ethereal jaunt</a></em></span> (caster level 15th).</p>
        </div>
        <div class="simplesect" lang="en">
          <div class="titlepage"/>
          <a name="id2131058"/>
          <div class="keywordset" style="display:none">
            <div class="keyword">other</div>
          </div>
          <a class="indexterm" name="MonstersO-R83"/>
          <p><span class="strong"><strong>Poison (Ex):</strong></span> Injury, Fortitude DC 17, initial and secondary damage 1d8 Con. The save DC is Constitution-based.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="simplesect" lang="en">
          <div class="titlepage"/>
          <a name="id2131087"/>
          <div class="keywordset" style="display:none">
            <div class="keyword">other</div>
          </div>
          <a class="indexterm" name="MonstersO-R84"/>
          <p><span class="strong"><strong>Skills:</strong></span> A <a href="ch70s10.html#MonstersO-R80">phase spider</a> has a +8 racial bonus on <a href="ch16s03.html#CombinedSkills71">Climb</a> checks and can always choose to take 10 on a <a href="ch16s03.html#CombinedSkills71">Climb</a> check, even if rushed or threatened.</p>
